<?xml version="1.0"?><?mso-application progid="Excel.Sheet"?><Workbook xmlns="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:spreadsheet" xmlns:o="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" xmlns:x="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:excel" xmlns:ss="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:spreadsheet" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40"><DocumentProperties xmlns="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office"><LastAuthor>Luis Ferreira</LastAuthor><LastSaved>2019-08-15T13:11:05Z</LastSaved><Version>16.00</Version></DocumentProperties><OfficeDocumentSettings xmlns="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office"><AllowPNG/></OfficeDocumentSettings><ExcelWorkbook xmlns="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:excel"><WindowHeight>5640</WindowHeight><WindowWidth>15345</WindowWidth><WindowTopX>32767</WindowTopX><WindowTopY>32767</WindowTopY><ProtectStructure>False</ProtectStructure><ProtectWindows>False</ProtectWindows></ExcelWorkbook><Styles><Style ss:ID="Default" ss:Name="Normal"><Alignment ss:Vertical="Bottom"/><Borders/><Font ss:FontName="Calibri" x:Family="Swiss" ss:Size="11" ss:Color="#000000"/><Interior/><NumberFormat/><Protection/></Style><Style ss:ID="s62"><Alignment ss:Vertical="Top" ss:WrapText="1"/></Style></Styles><Worksheet ss:Name="Script"><Table x:FullColumns="1" x:FullRows="1" ss:StyleID="s62" ss:DefaultColumnWidth="242.25" ss:DefaultRowHeight="15"><Column ss:StyleID="s62" ss:Width="189"/><Column ss:StyleID="s62" ss:Width="117.75"/><Column ss:StyleID="s62" ss:AutoFitWidth="0" ss:Width="281.25"/><Column ss:StyleID="s62" ss:Width="147.75"/><Column ss:StyleID="s62" ss:Width="243"/><Column ss:StyleID="s62" ss:Width="120"/><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="75"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">WILDLIFE_UNITPROPERTIES_DLC03</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">The DEV TEAM / MISC NOTES column contains info on what text between { } signs means (if applicable). It usually stands for either a numeric value, or a numeric value with an icon. Text between [ ] signs stands for a certain type of icon. </Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SCENE ID</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">TEXT ID</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ENGLISH STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">LOCALIZED STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ALTERNATIVE ENGLISH STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ALTERNATIVE LOCALIZED STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">LOCALIZATION NOTES</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DEV TEAM / MISC NOTES</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">INFECTIOUS_CHOMP</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Infectious Chomp</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Zakaźny gryz</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">INFECTIOUS_CHOMP</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">A melee attack.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Atak wręcz.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">CONSUME_CORPSE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Consume Corpse</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Spożycie zwłok</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="75"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">CONSUME_CORPSE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Eat the corpse of target Biological or Cyborg unit. This unit heals for {HealAmount}[hp/], and gains a stack of [abilityblue]Feast[/abilityBlue]: {DamageIncrease}% increased damage and Fast movement speed for {Duration}[turn/]. This buff can stack up to {StackAmount} times.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Powoduje skonsumowanie wskazanej jednostki organicznej lub cyborga. Jednostka konsumująca odzyskuje {HealAmount}[hp/] i zyskuje jeden poziom [abilityblue]uczty[/abilityBlue]: wzrost zadawanych obrażeń o {DamageIncrease}% i szybki ruch na {Duration}[turn/]. Efekt ten może się sumować do {StackAmount} razy.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">CONSUME_CORPSE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PROP_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Feast</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Uczta</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">CONSUME_CORPSE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PROP_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Unit has {DamageIncrease}% increased damage per stack as well as Fast movement speed.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Jednostka zadaje obrażenia większe o {DamageIncrease}% na każdy poziom i ma szybki ruch.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">RANCID_STENCH</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Rancid Stench</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Odór zgnilizny</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="45"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">RANCID_STENCH</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">At the end of this unit's turn, adjacent enemy ground Biological and Cyborg units become [abilityred]Poisoned[/abilityred].</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Na koniec tury tej jednostki sąsiadujące wrogie naziemne jednostki organiczne i cyborgów zostają [abilityred]zatrute[/abilityred].</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">RABID_BITE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Rabid Bite</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Wściekłe ugryzienie</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">RABID_BITE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">A melee bite attack.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Atak wręcz polegający na ugryzieniu.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GASTRIC_JUICES</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Gastric Juices</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Soki trawienne</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GASTRIC_JUICES</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Vomit armor melting gastric acids at a target.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Obryzguje cel wymiotami roztwarzającymi pancerz za pomocą kwasów żołądkowych.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PHANTOM_CLAW</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Phantom Claw</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Widmowy szpon</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PHANTOM_CLAW</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">A swipe with a psionically charged claw.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Cios naładowanym psionicznie pazurem.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">FORESHADOW_MADNESS</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Foreshadow Madness</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Zwiastun szaleństwa</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">FORESHADOW_MADNESS</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Attack a target with Psionic force and attempt to foresee and bring about an ominous madness.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Atakuje cel siłą psioniczną i próbuje sprowadzić nań fatalny obłęd.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="75"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">FORESHADOW_MADNESS</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">STATUS_EFFECT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">{ForeseeChance}[strengthPsyche/] strength chance of applying [abilityred]Approaching Madness[/abilityred] to target non-Mindless unit, for {ForeshadowDuration}[turn/].  If resisted, apply [abilityred]Broken Mind[/abilityred] instead.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Szansa (siła {ForeseeChance}[strengthPsyche/]) na spowodowanie [abilityred]bliskiego szaleństwa[/abilityred] u wskazanej jednostki nienależącej do bezmózgich, na {ForeshadowDuration}[turn/]. W razie odparcia wywołuje w zamian [abilityred]załamanie umysłowe[/abilityred].</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">FORESHADOW_MADNESS</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PROP_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Approaching Madness</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Bliskie szaleństwo</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="45"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">FORESHADOW_MADNESS</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PROP_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">This unit will receive [abilityred]Catatonic[/abilityred], [abilityred]Insanity[/abilityred] or [abilityred]Panic[/abilityred] at the end of its turn.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ta jednostka zostanie dotknięta [abilityred]katatonią[/abilityred], [abilityred]obłędem[/abilityred] lub [abilityred]paniką[/abilityred] na koniec swojej tury.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SHADOW_JUMP</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Shadow Jump</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Skok w cień</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="60"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SHADOW_JUMP</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">This unit teleports to target hex within {HexRange} hexes and wraps itself in shadows, gaining [abilityblue]Complete Immunity[/abilityblue] for {ShadowJumpDuration}[turn/].</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ta jednostka teleportuje się na wskazane pole w promieniu {HexRange} pól i kryje się w cieniach, zyskując [abilityblue]pełną niewrażliwość[/abilityblue] na {ShadowJumpDuration}[turn/].</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SHADOW_JUMP</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PROP_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Intangible Shadows</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Niematerialne cienie</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SHADOW_JUMP</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PROP_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">This unit cannot be affected by any Damage Channel, Status Effect or Hazard Effects.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ta jednostka nie doznaje żadnych obrażeń i nie odczuwa wpływu efektów stanu ani zagrożeń.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">AURA_OF_BAD_LUCK</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Aura of Misfortune</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Aura nieszczęścia</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">AURA_OF_BAD_LUCK</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Adjacent units to this one have a {FumbleChance}% chance to Fumble their attacks.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sąsiadujące jednostki mają {FumbleChance}% szans na spudłowanie.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">AURA_OF_BAD_LUCK</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PROP_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">This unit is in an aura of bad luck and has an extra {FumbleChance}% Fumble chance.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ta jednostka znajduje się w zasięgu aury pecha i ma dodatkowe {FumbleChance}% szans na spudłowanie.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">In the text below, text refers to a person that can either be male or female. If relevant for translation, please use the ‘localized string’ column for the male text and the ‘alternative localized string’ column for the female text. You and Your might be examples of this.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">In the text below, any inserted strings - anything of the form {text} - is replaced by an integer value for the thing described in the brackets. If the {text} is not followed by a unit - e.g. shields, hitpoints - the icon for the unit is inserted together with the integer. The same holds for symbols - e.g. '+', '%' - which are occasionally inserted together with the integer.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">For references to game terminology and in-world references, please check the glossary delivered as part of the documentation.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell></Row><Row><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell></Row><Row><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell></Row><Row><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell></Row><Row><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell></Row><Row><Cell>